Description:
&quot;Sophie, a quiet and plain girl working in a hat shop, finds her life thrown into turmoil when she is literally swept off her feet by a mysterious but handsome wizard named Howl. The vain and vengeful Witch of the Waste, jealous of their friendship, puts a curse on Sophie. To her horror, Sophie discovers the spell has turned her into an elderly woman. She then embarks on an incredible odyssey to lift the curse and enters a magical world where fires talk, dogs spy for their wizard owners, and a ramshackle castle wanders across the countryside.&quot;

Features:
This is a mutliple audio release including: 
Japanese, English, French, Cantonese, Mandarin
[5.1 LC-AAC (Japanese), 2ch LC-AAC (English),
2ch HE-AAC (French, Cantonese, Mandarin)]
Subtitled in the following languages:
English (SSA, SRT, Vobsub), Titles and Signs (SSA, SRT), Japanese, French, Cantonese, Mandarin (Vobsub)

